    <note>Hu(1) Jue [17718] See documentation for son-in-law, Han(1) Guohua [651]. Jue served in the administration of the Meng(2) rulers of Sichuan and when Taizu pacified Shu, he moved to Kaifeng where his daughter was born and died soon after. She was raised in the home of her mother, born Li(2). From the time of Jue's great grandfather, the family was hereditarily rich, noble, and powerful (shi fu, gui, hao).</note>
